    metaDescription: "As AI rapidly transforms education and labor markets globally, governments and institutions like California, India, and leading universities accelerate policy and initiatives to prepare workforces and students for an AI-driven future amid job displacement warnings.",
    slug: "ai-education-workforce-policy-future",
