    investorTakeaways: ["SpaceX stock is trading below its initial public offering (IPO) price, surprising many market observers.", "Reports indicate some early investors and insiders have sold shares, contributing to market jitters.", "The current volatility contrasts sharply with earlier optimistic valuations that suggested SpaceX could rival Amazon's market cap."],
