    featuredImagePrompt: "A dynamic, industry-specific visual representing India's economic volatility. Focus on a stylized depiction of the Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE) building or a modern Indian financial district skyline. Overlay digital elements: a graph showing sharp upward and downward trends for Sensex/Nifty, an exchange rate display showing 'USD-INR 95', and abstract glowing arrows indicating market movement. Integrate subtle hints of IPO documents or digital trading interfaces. The overall mood should convey both challenge and opportunity, with vibrant colors against a sophisticated financial backdrop. Ensure the composition is unique and does not resemble typical stock photos, focusing on an energetic, complex, Indian-centric financial landscape.",
