    risks: ["Continued reduction in on-chain liquidity due to stablecoin market cap contraction.", "Potential for Bitcoin to break below the $58,000 power law support line if macro headwinds intensify.", "Increased regulatory scrutiny and potential restrictions on crypto assets in various jurisdictions, as seen in Pakistan.", "Absence of new capital inflows or significant positive catalysts to drive market recovery.", "Macroeconomic factors, such as high interest rates or inflation, dampening investor appetite for risk assets."],
