    socialHeadlines: ["Big news! The SEC is exploring new crypto ETFs, while Visa & Mastercard back a new stablecoin. Plus, Nasdaq is bringing its data on-chain! #Crypto #TradFi", "Institutional crypto adoption is heating up! 🔥 SEC, Visa, Nasdaq are all in. What does this mean for the future of finance? #Blockchain #ETFs #Stablecoins", "Wall Street is going crypto! From new ETFs to stablecoins & on-chain data, see how major players are integrating digital assets. #DeFi #CryptoNews", "The lines are blurring: SEC, Visa/Mastercard, and Nasdaq are pushing crypto into the mainstream. Get the full breakdown. #FinancialMarkets #Web3", "Don\'t miss it! Key developments from the SEC, Visa, and Nasdaq are signaling a new era for crypto. Read our analysis! #DigitalAssets #Investment"],
