      priceMovement: "As a stablecoin, OUSD is designed to maintain a 1:1 peg with the U.S. dollar. Price movements are expected to be minimal, primarily reflecting temporary de-pegs due to market liquidity or arbitrage opportunities.",
      onChainMetrics: "Specific on-chain metrics are not available for a newly launched token. Key metrics to monitor in the future would include active addresses, transaction count, stablecoin velocity, and distribution across wallets to gauge adoption.",
