      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "The most probable outcome is a continued \'arms race\' in MEV, with both offensive and defensive strategies becoming more sophisticated. There\'s a high probability of increased focus on security and MEV mitigation from protocol developers, alongside persistent, albeit evolving, bot activity. Overall sentiment impact is likely medium-term neutral, with short-term caution.",
